Class OStack<T>

java.lang.Object
  lib.OStack<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
CheckerConstants.StateStack, CommonMoveStack, GoConstants.StateStack, HexConstants.StateStack, RectangleStack, sgf_gamestack, SimpleGroup, SpriteStack, StringStack
public abstract class OStack<T>
extends java.lang.Object

this is a light weight replacement for Vector. It is not thread safe, and it has no compatibility problems with java 1.1. Some of it's behavior is not strictly stack-like or identical to Vector.

Author:
ddyer
